          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "“Have I looked at the sun shining in the skies, or the moon walking down its silver pathway, "
